description: Manuel Deboxer is now in charge of our casting crew. He hasn't been in the business for a while so he's got some catching up to do. His first task is to personally meet with our models and decide if he wants them or not to make future appearances. No one's job is safe! In addition, Deboxer's skills are so good that it is very difficult for anyone to disobey him. Gotta please Deboxer or else you're out!
title: HypnoCasting - Marc, Scene #01
